data.description: Low maintenance living in West Wichita! This 3 bedroom, 1 1/2 bathroom home includes vinyl siding, updated vinyl windows, hardwood floors, updated electrical and new AC unit. The home features spacious rooms, vaulted ceiling in the living room and a dining area that is open to the kitchen and living room. The kitchen offers updated cabinets, plenty of countertop space and extra storage. The fenced yard, covered patio and private courtyard are great for relaxing. There is an oversized one car detached garage with a storage room and attached carport as well as a storage shed with electricity. Conveniently located in a nice west Wichita neighborhood near shopping and restaurants.
